com.interpss.core.aclf.impl.func

Class AclfBusYMatrixHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.interpss.core.aclf.impl.func.BaseAclfBusHelper
      • com.interpss.core.aclf.impl.func.AclfBusYMatrixHelper

  • public class AclfBusYMatrixHelper
extends BaseAclfBusHelper
    This class provides methods to calculate the Y or J-matrix elements for a bus in an AC load flow model. It extends the BaseAclfBusHelper class and provides specific implementations for calculating the diagonal elements of the Y or J-matrix, including the self admittance and the Jacobian matrix.
